
This ruby gem is for accessing the Pearson Powerschool API.


Usage:

Add to your Gemfile:

  gem 'powerschool', git: 'git@github.com/tomk32/powerschool.git'


As you might be on a different Powerschool Partner server, you can change the URL in your initializer:

  Powerschool::Client.base_uri 'https://partner3.powerschool.com'

